lecho.lib.hellocharts.computator

Class PreviewChartComputator

  • java.lang.Object
    • lecho.lib.hellocharts.computator.ChartComputator
      • lecho.lib.hellocharts.computator.PreviewChartComputator

  • public class PreviewChartComputator
extends ChartComputator
    Version of ChartComputator for preview charts. It always uses maxViewport as visible viewport and currentViewport as preview area.
